An earth warrior (elite) is an elite version of the earth warrior. If on a Slayer assignment, an elite Earth warrior is guaranteed to spawn; otherwise, elite monsters have a spawn rate of 1 in 1,000. Elite spawn rates can be further increased with the use of fellstalk incense sticks.
